A PTA meeting of unified board members, courageous school leaders, loyal educators, committed community members and success seeking students. WE ARE HAZLEHURST. WE ARE INDIANS. WE ARE ENOUGH! #excellenceistheexpectation #seeyouatthetop
#hcsd

post_text: The Hazlehurst City School District served as one of the partners for the 2019 Hazlehurst Community Back to School Bash. This year’s theme was One Team One Goal No Limits. Mayor Sandifer, City Officials, and Community Members partnered together to host a wonderful day out for the entire family. There was entertainment, food, a water slide, horseback riding, and face painting. Most importantly, a host of sponsors provided book bags, paper, pencils, and other school supplies for the students in the community. Thanks to all of the planners, vendors, sponsors, and volunteers for making the 2019 Back to School Bash a great success.
